Greetings from *Center for Innovation*, *CFI*!

We invite coordinator applications for the Industry Connect Team, CFI.

A typical coordinator would get the chance to

   - Interact with illustrious alumni at the helm of companies
   - Represent CFI while interacting with executives from companies
   - Manage *innovative industrial projects* at CFI, with the possibility
   of generating *intellectual property*!


Get some hands-on techno-managerial experience as you delve into the world
of IPR, MoU's etc while managing projects and deadlines.

Want to be a part of the team??

